  "original_title": "SLT-MOBITEL revolutionises online experience for customers",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "SLT-MOBITEL revolutionises online experience for customers",
      "author": "Sahan Weerasooriya",
      "body_lines": [
        "Offering incredible convenience to customers, SLT-MOBITEL, the National ICT Solutions Provider, announced the unveiling of a new digital portal to obtain SLT-MOBITEL Fibre connections. The portal that can be accessed through www.sltmobitel.lk, provides an attractive solution to obtain a new fibre connection within a minimum time period.",
        "Customers can now process their new SLT-MOBITEL Fibre connection order promptly through the portal and will no longer require a visit to an SLT-MOBITEL Regional office. The portal also offers a user-friendly approach with a simple interface. Adding further value, new Fibre connections are offered at a discounted price of Rs. 10,000/- via the digital platform.",
        "Prabhath Dahanayake, Chief Marketing Officer of SLT said that, \u201cFibre is the backbone for the growth of digital Sri Lanka, and it is only natural that customers expect to be able to obtain their connections without relying on physical visits. Furthermore, SLT-MOBITEL is committed to make the customer experience and onboarding journey to be as seamless and easy as possible, considering the current restrictions on travel that many of them are facing at the moment. I invite customers to sign up with SLT-MOBITEL Fibre and enter a whole new world of digital acceleration.\u201d",
        "SOE reforms vital, although monetary policies to put SL\u2019s economy on right track are on \u2013 CBSL Governor",
        "Hela becomes the first apparel manufacturer to extend the globally-recognised P.A.C.E. program to Egypt",
        "Leave a Reply Cancel replyYour email address will not be published. Required fields are marked *Comment Name *",
        "Save my name, email, and website in this browser for the next time I comment."
      ],
